text: Þis is þara X hida landgemære æt Corsatune.
Ærest of Afene up andlang corsan on ecles cumb suðeweardne ðat west be wealle.
Eft syð be welle þær up ofer feld on ða riht landgemære on þone sidlingweg to wuda.
Of wuda be ecge on þa ðreo landgemære.
Þanon norð to wege on gerihte on wimundes stan.
Of þam stane norð andlang weges þær est of þam wege on gerihte to brynes cumb suðweardne.
Of ecge east on stanwell broc.
